Simple Image Share
------------------
This application is a single PHP script designed to drop into any web directory
and allow image uploading and sharing.

You can upload individual image files or .zip files containing any number of
images and directories. All images found in the .zip will be uploaded.

Dependencies
------------
* Mogrify executable. e.g. /usr/bin/mogrify
* Web server with PHP support.

INSTALL
-------
Edit the $mogrify variable in the configuration section.

Put the index.php script in a web accessible directory.

All images uploaded will be stored in images/photos in the same directory as
index.php.

